    <keyword>Pitch Centre Path of Cam</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">When a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower</text> is a Circular, we call it a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower-Roller</text> - the <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Pitch-Curve</text> is the locus of the center the roller around the <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Cam</text>. The <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Cam</text> would be this curve if the <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Cam-Roller</text> had a ZERO radius.</para>
        </td>
